{"tid":1488762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足 今晚過後 我地再一齊努力","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:22:58.000Z","uid":8131,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0bfda7bea4e5670d0b12e7a3bd40101bf74c33","tid":1488762,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"首先我唔會屌大家 <br />\n今晚呢一邊箱大家係到研究梗Madam對波係咪假嘅時候 係live睇梗巴打找數嘅時候 係另一邊箱 澳門嘅手足 為大家發聲為大家默站 仲俾澳門警犬搭咗7個人<br />\n<br />\n希望大家今晚過後 瞓醒覺 再次燃起心入面團火 唔好唔記得我地俾人拉咗 七百幾個手足 6個手足犧牲咗 一個女手足俾狗打爆咗一隻眼 仲有好多冇哂聲氣唔知仲係唔係係醫院昏迷梗嘅手足 <br />\n<br />\n求大家要丁嘅丁夠 唔好再follow再討論 運動過後我理撚得你叫雞又好援交又好 屌madam就唔好啦 大家focus返！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n還我香港淨土"},{"pid":"2cbe371f597d3c084b6778481334484664822f71","tid":1488762,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"733546820c888cb430ee9f78101f07d2d8afcc77","tid":1488762,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"大家呢兩個月都緊張咗咁耐 可能連丁都冇心情打 見到個大婆少少嘅Madam就抑壓唔住 非常理解 丁完好專注返係呢場革命到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306f70a0d9e0abc772886064db709c4c6bd353da","tid":1488762,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"示威者 全敗vs全勝 政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分和勇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭之路</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">刻不容緩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ohp63ms.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhp63ms.png&h=835c3fe2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c67f068e1b49b4fafd3a91a2557d8be6fd8d4e56","tid":1488762,"uid":167132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港！！！"},{"pid":"6a6d2d00562690075293c8b096089cf58c2accce","tid":1488762,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"【22:50】澳門一名獨立記者報道，當地治安警表示，今晚有7名可疑者被帶返警區進一步調查，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">包括4名澳門居民、2名內地居民及1名香港居民</span></span></strong>。另外，有記者拍到，晚上8時多，多名治安警圍着一男一女，不讓兩人離開，稱在他們的書包中搜出數張「貼紙」，兩人最後被10多名警員帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【21:55】《逃犯條例》反修例風波在港引發連場警民衝突，澳門早前有人擬於今晚（19日）在澳門新馬路噴水池發起「8‧19默站」，反對香港警察使用暴力對待市民，被當地警方發出不批准指示。《澳門力報》報道，今晚約8時，澳門議事亭前地已有多名警員駐守，檢查多名在場者的身分證，又帶走不少人調查，當中大部分人穿白色衣服。"},{"pid":"60395c76f748ac1c9c1455ce75ce3cef85e28958","tid":1488762,"uid":280934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"嘈完就算<br />\n要重新上路<br />\n大把正經野做"},{"pid":"0b0bafa6d2e2c986b181cf8f0d5c5c49c808aa99","tid":1488762,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68913bab98ece474321438d0ae77d4e332003e4","tid":1488762,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:52:18.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再屌手足啦 佢地都係人 按奈唔住自己嘅本性 等佢地丁完聽朝就會自動歸位架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a3a12b5ea84020e5c286b677928c9fecf24fbb","tid":1488762,"uid":8131,"like":0